[Part cii]
- M1: their length x their perpendicular height oe. If not 6 and 3 their dimensions need to be verifiable eg shown on the diagram. eg M0 for sqrt(13) or 3.6... etc as their perpendicular height. oe includes two triangles + the 4x3 rectangle or the 8x3 rectangle - two triangles. Need to be certain that 3 is slant height to withhold the marks
- M1: 18 nfww

